Veteran Nollywood actor, Dan Nkoloagu is dead. The news of his death was announced by his son, Dan Nkoloagu Jnr on Facebook. According to his son who broke the news, Nkoloagu died on Friday, January 22, 2021. Until his death, Dan Nkoloagu had starred in several Nigerian movies alongside Nkem Owoh and the likes. He was popularly known for his Chief Priest cum Native Doctor movie roles